အရာတၞဟ်ခြာဂှ် အလဵုဇကု အစာကဗျ ဗာန် ထပ်ချူလဝ် ဒှ်မာန်ရ။ <ref name="lindsay">{{cite book |last = Lindsay |first = Maurice |author-link = Maurice Lindsay |title = The Burns Encyclopedia |origyear = 1959 |url = http://www.robertburns.org/encyclopedia/index.shtml |access-date = 28 December 2007 |edition = New Third |date = December 1996 |publisher = Robert Hale Ltd. |location =  |isbn = 0-7090-5719-9 |page =  |chapter = Auld Lang Syne |chapter-url = http://www.robertburns.org/encyclopedia/AuldLangSyne.5.shtml |ref = }}</ref>
စပ်ကဵု မထဗိုန် မဒယှေ်ဒၟံင်လၟုဟ်ဂှ် ဒှ်မထဗိုန် နူကဵု ခေတ် ဗာန်တေအ်ရဟာဂှ် ဟွံတီကၠးကၠးရ။ ဆဂး မထဗိုန်ဂှ် စကာဒၟံင် ပ္ဍဲသကတ်လာန်ကီု သီုကဵု ပ္ဍဲကဵု ဂၠးတိ ဒၞာဲတၞဟ်တအ်ရ။<ref name="ScotlandOrgRef">{{cite web |url = https://www.scotland.org/features/the-history-and-words-of-auld-lang-syne/ |title = The History and Words of Auld Lang Syne |work = Scotland.org |date =  |access-date = 1 January 2012 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author = Traditional |url = http://www.ukmagic.co.uk/song_scottish/auld_lang_syne.html |title = Auld Lang Syne |work = Traditional Songs from Scotland |publisher = Ukmagic.co.uk |year = 2006 |access-date = 1 January 2012 }}</ref>

ဒွက်ဏအ်ဂှ် ပ္ဍဲအခိင် မကၠောန်သဘင် မဒးသြာဲခြာ၊ ဟွံသေင်မ္ဂး ပ္ဍဲသဘင်သၞာံတၟိတုဲ ဒှ်အာအခိုက် သကတ်မွဲကီု သီုကဵု ဒေသတၞဟ် ပ္ဍဲကဵု ဗြိတိန်ရ။ နူဂှ် ပြးအာ အလုံလိုက်မွဲရ။

